OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSacked teacher loses legal 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbid in trans pupil case    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A teacher who refused to call a        
OL,6, transgender pupil by their preferred   
OL,7, name and pronouns has lost a bid to    
OL,8, launch a legal challenge against their 
OL,9, school.                                
OL,11,FShe said she had safeguarding concerns 
OL,12,Fabout the school's support of the      
OL,13,Fchild, described in court as a         
OL,14,F"transgender-affirming approach".      
OL,16,FThe campaign group Christian Concern,  
OL,17,Fwhich supported the teacher, said she  
OL,18,Fwas then sacked for gross misconduct   
OL,19,Fafter sharing information about the    
OL,20,Fchild while taking legal advice.       
